
@startuml
' Facepage Class Diagram

class User {
  -id: String
  -name: String
  -email: String
  -dateOfBirth: Date
}

class Account {
  -accountNumber: String
  -type: Enum (Personal, Business)
  +createPage(): Page
}

class PersonalAccount {
  +sendFriendRequest(user: User): void
  +acceptFriendRequest(user: User): void
}

class BusinessAccount {
  -monthlyFee: Double
  +createAdPage(): AdPage
}

class Page {
  -name: String
  -visits: Integer
  +grantPrivileges(account: Account): void
}

class AdPage extends Page {
  -bounceRate: Double
  -clickThroughRate: Double
  -conversionRate: Double
}

class FriendRequest {
  -fromUser: User
  -toUser: User
  -status: Enum (Pending, Accepted, Rejected)
}

' Associations and Relationships

User "1" -- "1" Account : owns
Account "1" -- "0..*" Page : creates
Account "1" -- "0..*" FriendRequest : sends
Page "1" -- "1" Account : administeredBy
Page "1" -- "0..*" AdPage : extends?

' Inheritance

Account <|-- PersonalAccount
Account <|-- BusinessAccount
Page <|-- AdPage

' Constraints and Notes

note right of User
  Each user has exactly one account.
  A user cannot have more than one account.
end note

note right of Account
  An account is uniquely identified by account number.
end note

note right of Page
  No two pages under the same account can have the same name.
end note

note right of AdPage
  Only business accounts can create ad pages.
end note

note right of FriendRequest
  Only personal accounts can send or receive friend requests.
end note

@enduml

### Explanation of Key Elements:

- **User**: Represents a person joining Facepage. Each user has a unique ID.
- **Account**: Base class for both `PersonalAccount` and `BusinessAccount`. Identified by an automatically generated account number.
- **PersonalAccount**: Extends `Account`. Can send/receive friend requests.
- **BusinessAccount**: Extends `Account`. Has a monthly fee and can create advertisement pages.
- **Page**: General page created by any account. Each account can create multiple pages with unique names.
- **AdPage**: Subclass of `Page`, used for advertising. Tracks bounce rate, click-through rate, and conversion rate.
- **FriendRequest**: Represents a request to add someone as a friend. Only applicable to personal accounts.

